# Plan 10: Events/Tour Dates Section

## Goal
Create the "Tour" or "Events" page to display upcoming and past shows.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/tour/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Create an `EventRow` component (date, venue, city, ticket button).
- [ ] Fetch events from the database, separating "Upcoming" and "Past".
- [ ] Add "Add to Calendar" functionality (generate .ics file or Google Calendar link).
- [ ] Embed a Google Map showing the location of the next upcoming show (optional).
